Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.07,0:09:33.92,zh,,0,0,0,,所以呢？你还是会有感情吧？\N{\ren}And what? That means you don't have feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.00,0:09:37.14,zh,,0,0,0,,听着，我很懂你，你很有能力\N{\ren}Listen, it takes a Chutback to know one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.21,0:09:39.02,zh,,0,0,0,,但你若不了解自己，那又怎样？\N{\ren}You got all this power but what good is it if you don't even know who you are?
