Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.28,0:12:16.75,zh,,0,0,0,,但谁也别想拿我当笑柄\N{\ren}But nobody raises hell at my expense!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.83,0:12:18.46,zh,,0,0,0,,天啊，你冷静点…\N{\ren}Oh, goddammit. Easy! Easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.54,0:12:20.51,zh,,0,0,0,,杰瑞，怎么了吗，兄弟？\N{\ren}Jerry, what seems to be the problem here, pal?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.58,0:12:23.02,zh,,0,0,0,,我不是你的兄弟，只是你的笑柄\N{\ren}I'm not your pal, I'm your punchline.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.35,0:12:24.69,zh,,0,0,0,,我听到他们说的话了\N{\ren}I heard these assholes talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.77,0:12:27.28,zh,,0,0,0,,我知道他们都在嘲笑我\N{\ren}I know I'm some grand joke for their amusement.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.36,0:12:28.41,zh,,0,0,0,,你太可恶了，瑞克\N{\ren}This was low, Rick, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.49,0:12:30.67,zh,,0,0,0,,但我老婆更可恶\N{\ren}I guess my wife can go even lower.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.74,0:12:33.68,zh,,0,0,0,,杰瑞，我能理解，但我们是在玩\N{\ren}Jerry, I get how this may have looked but we were just having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.76,0:12:34.85,zh,,0,0,0,,你们把我当笑柄\N{\ren}At my expense!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.93,0:12:37.98,zh,,0,0,0,,老公，我就喜欢你这么逊\N{\ren}Honey, no, I love you for being lame in a different way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.06,0:12:40.36,zh,,0,0,0,,为什么就没人喜欢真正的我呢？\N{\ren}Why can't anyone just love me for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.44,0:12:41.99,zh,,0,0,0,,他好扫兴，瑞克\N{\ren}He's bumming us out, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.07,0:12:43.21,zh,,0,0,0,,他再这样下去\N{\ren}If he can't deliver,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.29,0:12:45.34,zh,,0,0,0,,我们就得自己找乐子了\N{\ren}we'll have to make our own fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.90,0:12:54.41,zh,,0,0,0,,天啊，如果死在这辆车上\N{\ren}Oh my god, if I die in this car,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.49,0:12:55.54,zh,,0,0,0,,我就要自杀\N{\ren}I'm going to kill myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.35,0:13:06.32,zh,,0,0,0,,我以身为战争机器为荣\N{\ren}I'm now proud to be a war machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.40,0:13:08.54,zh,,0,0,0,,我不想变成别的样子了\N{\ren}I don't want to be anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.61,0:13:09.96,zh,,0,0,0,,很遗憾你的结论是这样\N{\ren}Hate that this is your takeaway!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.03,0:13:12.25,zh,,0,0,0,,嘿，这达不到我的标准\N{\ren}Yo, this does not cut the Chut!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.33,0:13:15.56,zh,,0,0,0,,－我不想死　－或许我们不用死\N{\ren}- I don't want to die! - Maybe we don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.77,0:13:20.40,zh,,0,0,0,,－杰瑞　－真可惜\N{\ren}- Jerry! - A pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.48,0:13:23.21,zh,,0,0,0,,杰瑞原本很好玩的\N{\ren}Jerry was once a wellspring of nuanced flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.29,0:13:25.55,zh,,0,0,0,,你们却毁了我们的玩具\N{\ren}But you've gone and ruined our toy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.63,0:13:28.39,zh,,0,0,0,,所以我们决定要带他走\N{\ren}Which is why he's coming with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.60,0:13:32.74,zh,,0,0,0,,该死，贝丝\N{\ren}Goddamnit, Beth
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.82,0:13:34.79,zh,,0,0,0,,我们不该跟着恶魔去其他地方的\N{\ren}you never follow hell-demons to a second location.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.86,0:13:36.25,zh,,0,0,0,,因为一定是地狱\N{\ren}It's always hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.96,0:13:40.64,zh,,0,0,0,,今天充满了痛苦\N{\ren}A great day for suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.72,0:13:44.37,zh,,0,0,0,,－所以很糟　－所以很棒\N{\ren}- Which is the worst day. - Which is the best day!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.32,0:13:48.29,zh,,0,0,0,,好，如果被发现，我们就完蛋了，配合我演出\N{\ren}OK, if these guys catch us, we're screwed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.37,0:13:49.88,zh,,0,0,0,,我们很快就能救回你的蠢老公\N{\ren}So follow my lead and we'll have your idiot husband back in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.95,0:13:51.76,zh,,0,0,0,,你只是不爽要穿旗鱼装\N{\ren}You're just moody you got stuck with the marlin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.83,0:13:54.61,zh,,0,0,0,,不对，我是不爽你搞砸我的好事\N{\ren}Wrong. I'm moody because you toyed with my shit and broke it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:56.15,zh,,0,0,0,,旗鱼装已经是不幸中的大幸\N{\ren}The marlin's the best thing about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.23,0:13:57.66,zh,,0,0,0,,好，我确实有点过分\N{\ren}OK, fine, I got a little carried away
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.73,0:13:58.83,zh,,0,0,0,,但杰瑞不是你的玩具\N{\ren}but Jerry is not your toy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.98,0:14:00.70,zh,,0,0,0,,我们得来这里都是因为你搞砸了\N{\ren}We're here because you fucked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.91,0:14:04.51,zh,,0,0,0,,旗鱼肚、飞镖靶脸\N{\ren}Marlin Guts. Dartboard Face.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.59,0:14:06.39,zh,,0,0,0,,这应该是你们的名字没错\N{\ren}I assume those are your names and yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.47,0:14:08.52,zh,,0,0,0,,但你们不在我的名单上\N{\ren}they are not on my list.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.60,0:14:11.32,zh,,0,0,0,,被地狱拒于门外好痛苦\N{\ren}Oh, the pain of being rejected from hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.39,0:14:13.96,zh,,0,0,0,,好痛苦，所以我好喜欢\N{\ren}Oh, it's painful so I love it, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.03,0:14:16.09,zh,,0,0,0,,谢谢，我好开心\N{\ren}Oh, such pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.16,0:14:18.60,zh,,0,0,0,,我不是有意要让你开心的\N{\ren}I didn't mean to cause you any pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.67,0:14:22.31,zh,,0,0,0,,我很痛苦，所以我很开心\N{\ren}Which causes me pain. Which gives me pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.39,0:14:25.66,zh,,0,0,0,,那就别让我进去最好，衣帽架脸\N{\ren}Then thrill me by keeping me out, Coat Hanger Face.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.74,0:14:28.38,zh,,0,0,0,,天啊，我是衣帽架头\N{\ren}Wow. It's Coat Rack Head.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.49,0:14:33.10,zh,,0,0,0,,但我们冒犯你不是很棒吗？\N{\ren}But, like, if we offend you, isn't that good?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.18,0:14:36.03,zh,,0,0,0,,那当然，我很喜欢\N{\ren}Big time, yeah, duh. I loved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:39.70,zh,,0,0,0,,我很痛苦，所以很快乐\N{\ren}So painful, and therefore so pleasurable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.78,0:14:40.95,zh,,0,0,0,,好，请进\N{\ren}Yeah, go on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.80,0:14:48.10,zh,,0,0,0,,瑞克、贝丝，你们果然是爱我的\N{\ren}Rick, Beth, you love me after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.18,0:14:50.78,zh,,0,0,0,,我爱她，她爱你，但我不爱你\N{\ren}I love her, she loves you. Those credits don't transfer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.93,0:14:53.84,zh,,0,0,0,,瑞克，我们正希望你会来\N{\ren}Rick, we were so hoping you'd come down here
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.91,0:14:56.59,zh,,0,0,0,,这样我们会爽歪歪\N{\ren}so we could come down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.66,0:14:57.89,zh,,0,0,0,,我们是来救杰瑞的\N{\ren}We're here to rescue Jerry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.96,0:15:01.39,zh,,0,0,0,,不对，你们是被我骗来的\N{\ren}No, you're here 'cause we want you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.48,0:15:07.83,zh,,0,0,0,,－好棒　－好痛，所以好舒服\N{\ren}- Excellent! - That hurts. Which means it feels good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.91,0:15:10.21,zh,,0,0,0,,－爸？　－你不明白吗，瑞克？\N{\ren}- Um, Dad? - Don't you see, Rick?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.29,0:15:14.69,zh,,0,0,0,,杰瑞只是诱饵，你们是一体的\N{\ren}Jerry was just bait. The two of you, you're a package deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.76,0:15:15.90,zh,,0,0,0,,你在讲什么？\N{\ren}What the hell are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.98,0:15:18.70,zh,,0,0,0,,你觉得杰瑞很逊，自己很酷\N{\ren}You think Jerry is lame and you're cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.77,0:15:21.79,zh,,0,0,0,,不过这种想法才是最逊的\N{\ren}But the lamest thing of all is thinking that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.86,0:15:26.52,zh,,0,0,0,,你们两个加起来才是逊上加逊\N{\ren}The two of you combined is what we call the lamest thing ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.59,0:15:27.98,zh,,0,0,0,,不…\N{\ren}Oh, no. No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.05,0:15:31.40,zh,,0,0,0,,天啊，我真是又意又外\N{\ren}Well, well, well, table for surprised, party of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.06,0:15:33.79,zh,,0,0,0,,没错，看到了吗？\N{\ren}Yes, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.87,0:15:36.47,zh,,0,0,0,,尴尬在真空内是无法存在的\N{\ren}Cringe cannot exist in a vacuum.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.54,0:15:38.18,zh,,0,0,0,,需要被观察才会存在\N{\ren}It needs to be observed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.25,0:15:41.27,zh,,0,0,0,,皮钩，把客人钩住\N{\ren}Skin hooks! Hook our guests!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.05,0:15:44.16,zh,,0,0,0,,这皮钩不错，是哪来的？\N{\ren}Nice hooks. Where'd you get them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.28,0:15:47.46,zh,,0,0,0,,我不是叫你们把皮钩换掉吗？\N{\ren}Didn't I say replace those goddamn hooks?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.53,0:15:48.58,zh,,0,0,0,,我忘了\N{\ren}I forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.66,0:15:51.51,zh,,0,0,0,,所以我很羞愧，所以我很骄傲\N{\ren}Which makes me embarrassed. Which makes me proud!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.25,0:15:53.35,zh,,0,0,0,,该死\N{\ren}Goddamnit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.43,0:15:56.99,zh,,0,0,0,,该让你们三个体会我们的怒气了\N{\ren}It's time for you three to finally feel our full wrath!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.23,0:15:59.95,zh,,0,0,0,,这样你会很开心吧？\N{\ren}Oh, you'd love that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.03,0:16:01.87,zh,,0,0,0,,那样你不就会很生气吗？\N{\ren}But wouldn't that mean you hate it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.71,0:16:03.76,zh,,0,0,0,,管他的，快跑\N{\ren}Screw it, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.94,0:16:14.16,zh,,0,0,0,,瑞克，你在干吗？\N{\ren}Rick, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.23,0:16:15.70,zh,,0,0,0,,快蹲下，我们会被发现的\N{\ren}Get down, we've barely escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.78,0:16:17.42,zh,,0,0,0,,对，我们救到杰瑞了，我们走吧\N{\ren}Yeah, we've got Jerry. Let's get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:20.01,zh,,0,0,0,,才不要，我真是受够这种鸟事了\N{\ren}Screw that! I'm done with this Addams Family bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.08,0:16:21.43,zh,,0,0,0,,我要彻底做个了结\N{\ren}This ends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:25.11,zh,,0,0,0,,有爸爸帮女儿朋友的照片按了赞\N{\ren}Hey, a dad just liked all his daughter's friends' photos on Instagram!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.94,0:16:30.29,zh,,0,0,0,,所以我需要帮助\N{\ren}Which means I need help!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.36,0:16:32.58,zh,,0,0,0,,所以我不需要帮助\N{\ren}Which means I don't need help!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:34.89,zh,,0,0,0,,危险驾驶\N{\ren}Reckless driving,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.97,0:16:38.11,zh,,0,0,0,,过失杀害男信箱人和女信箱人\N{\ren}manslaughter of Mailboxians and Femailboxians.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.18,0:16:39.90,zh,,0,0,0,,持有卡拉星水晶尘\N{\ren}Possession of Kalaxian crystal dust,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.98,0:16:42.71,zh,,0,0,0,,以及太空太浩种族屠杀\N{\ren}and the genocide of Space Tahoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.78,0:16:43.96,zh,,0,0,0,,－干　－我想回家\N{\ren}- Fuck! - I wanna go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.04,0:16:45.21,zh,,0,0,0,,我们帮你们指派了公设辩护人\N{\ren}We've assigned you a public defender.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.29,0:16:47.30,zh,,0,0,0,,叫艾莉森汉妮根，跟那演员无关\N{\ren}Her name is Allison Hannigan. No relation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.38,0:16:49.81,zh,,0,0,0,,我能跟委托人单独谈谈吗？\N{\ren}May I speak to my clients alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.26,0:16:53.16,zh,,0,0,0,,各位，是我，我是那辆车\N{\ren}Guys, it's me. The car.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.23,0:16:55.37,zh,,0,0,0,,我好像把晶片插在她头上？\N{\ren}Like what I did with the chip in her head?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.45,0:16:56.66,zh,,0,0,0,,她会有大碍吗？\N{\ren}Is she gonna be OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.74,0:16:58.75,zh,,0,0,0,,我跟他们谈好条件了\N{\ren}I cut a deal with the local authorities.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.83,0:17:00.84,zh,,0,0,0,,他们只需要一个人顶罪就好\N{\ren}They just need one of you to take the fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.92,0:17:01.97,zh,,0,0,0,,选恰贝吧\N{\ren}Make it Chutback,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:05.40,zh,,0,0,0,,他毁了你我的一天，他是寄生虫\N{\ren}he ruined your night, he ruined mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.48,0:17:08.08,zh,,0,0,0,,是反社会军人小孩，整天游荡\N{\ren}He's a parasite, a sociopath military brat
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.15,0:17:10.71,zh,,0,0,0,,到处改变不需要被改变的人\N{\ren}who wanders the earth changing people who don't need to be changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.78,0:17:13.05,zh,,0,0,0,,我们都知道自己是什么样的人\N{\ren}I knew who I was, you did too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.13,0:17:15.02,zh,,0,0,0,,恰贝出现前，我们都过得好好的\N{\ren}We were fine before Chutback.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.09,0:17:16.27,zh,,0,0,0,,别管他妈的标准了\N{\ren}So fuck the Chut.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.34,0:17:18.77,zh,,0,0,0,,就让他顶罪，结案\N{\ren}Let's pin it all on him. Case closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.52,0:17:22.16,zh,,0,0,0,,两位觉得呢？\N{\ren}Yo, guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.23,0:17:23.42,zh,,0,0,0,,布鲁斯，你蛮烂的\N{\ren}Bruce, you're kind of a drip.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.49,0:17:26.17,zh,,0,0,0,,但比自以为酷的人更糟的是？\N{\ren}But know what's worse than self-appointed cool kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.25,0:17:28.09,zh,,0,0,0,,就是看不起这种人的人\N{\ren}People who think they're better than they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.17,0:17:29.60,zh,,0,0,0,,对啊，我们被布鲁斯骗\N{\ren}Yeah, it's not Bruce's fault
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.67,0:17:31.14,zh,,0,0,0,,也不是他的错，对吧？\N{\ren}we fell for his act, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.22,0:17:33.24,zh,,0,0,0,,他其实也没有多做什么\N{\ren}He just kinda sat there,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.32,0:17:34.95,zh,,0,0,0,,是我们自己把不安投射在他身上\N{\ren}with a jaw slack enough for us to project our insecurities on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.03,0:17:36.46,zh,,0,0,0,,这是我们的错\N{\ren}I mean, that's on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.53,0:17:38.09,zh,,0,0,0,,我们不会抛下你，布鲁斯\N{\ren}We're not gonna bail on you, Bruce.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.16,0:17:40.30,zh,,0,0,0,,好吧，那只能来硬的了\N{\ren}Okey-dokey, we'll do it the hard way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.96,0:17:43.02,zh,,0,0,0,,－天啊　－他妈怎么回事？\N{\ren}What the fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.14,0:17:46.82,zh,,0,0,0,,把这里炸掉本来就行得通\N{\ren}I mean, blowing the place up was always an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.90,0:17:50.29,zh,,0,0,0,,我以为你们会喜欢不暴力的做法\N{\ren}I just thought you guys might enjoy a less violent plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.36,0:17:52.04,zh,,0,0,0,,看吧？你变了\N{\ren}See! You have changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.23,0:18:03.42,zh,,0,0,0,,爸，这是什么？\N{\ren}Dad, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.49,0:18:05.55,zh,,0,0,0,,痛苦转换反转矫正器\N{\ren}An Aversion-Converting Inversion Reverter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.62,0:18:08.26,zh,,0,0,0,,会发射浓缩欢愉痛苦反转弹片\N{\ren}It shoots concentrated pleasure-pain inverting shrapnel
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.34,0:18:11.56,zh,,0,0,0,,把痛苦造成的欢愉变回痛苦\N{\ren}which reverts the pleasure from pain back into the pain from pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.64,0:18:13.87,zh,,0,0,0,,我们要用百分百的真诚杀死他们\N{\ren}We're gonna kill them with a hundred percent sincerity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.94,0:18:16.75,zh,,0,0,0,,我们还需要一些尴尬来启动过程\N{\ren}We need an embarrassing level of it to jumpstart the process too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.82,0:18:18.58,zh,,0,0,0,,杰瑞，请做自己\N{\ren}So, Jerry, just be yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.66,0:18:19.71,zh,,0,0,0,,这就是你的解决办法？\N{\ren}That's your solution?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.79,0:18:21.01,zh,,0,0,0,,继续羞辱我？\N{\ren}Humiliating me more?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.08,0:18:22.39,zh,,0,0,0,,对，爸，这样很不公平\N{\ren}Yeah, Dad, that doesn't seem fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.46,0:18:24.61,zh,,0,0,0,,我知道我没什么资格说话\N{\ren}I mean, I know I shouldn't really talk right now
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.68,0:18:27.36,zh,,0,0,0,,但我至少能用性爱证明我爱杰瑞\N{\ren}but at least I can prove I love Jerry through sexual gratification.
